      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/national_general/2026/07/01/PUUNXCZLBNBKPM24IYSMLPZKEA/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
      <description/>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 14:37:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <content:encoded>&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img align="center" src="https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/chosun/6W7OP72D7JET3DXG2UQB4R32MU.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;small&gt;일러스트=김성규&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;운동화를 세탁할 때 비닐봉지를 활용해보자. 비닐봉지에 따뜻한 물과 세제를 넣고 운동화를 15분 정도 담가둔다. 꺼내서 헹구면 깨끗해진다. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</content:encoded>
    </item>
